sequenceDiagram
    participant Patient
    participant ChatUI as Chat UI
    participant ChatCtrl as Chat Controller
    participant RAG as RAG Pipeline
    participant KB as Knowledge Base
    participant LLM as LLM Model

    Patient->>ChatUI: Write Query
    ChatUI->>ChatCtrl: Send Query
    ChatCtrl->>RAG: Process(query)
    RAG->>KB: Retrieve Relevant Documents
    KB-->>RAG: Retrieved Docs
    RAG->>LLM: Generate Answer(docs + query)
    LLM-->>RAG: Final Answer
    RAG-->>ChatCtrl: Response
    ChatCtrl-->>ChatUI: Display Response
